precis:
Amendments to the VESSEL TRAFFIC SERVICES ZONES REGULATIONS which exempt
smaller fishing vessels and pleasure craft from the application of these
Regulations, change the reporting requirements for vessels intending to
enter or to depart a berth in a Vessel Traffic Services Zone, and change
the reporting requirements for non-routine reports.
